:0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:41:46.000Z","msg":"推呀大家"},{"pid":"183ffc55ce8b9cfae6ff1b3cd9efe5c61daf0054","tid":1840224,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:42:20.000Z","msg":"我做到嘅就係得咁多<br />\n對住佢地我真係好無力"},{"pid":"427d1ccea9247689cf8c2ae68c32b215797310ba","tid":1840224,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:44:00.000Z","msg":"Please !!!<br />\nTry all our method to save them and protect them"},{"pid":"7faadef88bf30cab5d7f87610c0175cdd4e6e54d","tid":1840224,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:48:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72e05fe1cf5643ac4a2b9eacad912a56445e0281","tid":1840224,"uid":162008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:52:26.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=c5e01ddb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f29352dc2c6db808b1c1349bacd4f66607c77671","tid":1840224,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703a47dfa5c66859be437de59d3f38ffac0a826f","tid":1840224,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a12dabecd90fd91e7f6adc48dd8e0b31cff3e05e","tid":1840224,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:46:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fe337be5d611b61d554df344fe1672175fae0e3","tid":1840224,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:46:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1715ed286d137195320ec4e061d0966f6346c24","tid":1840224,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:46:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f931a2121e81724d854c7b1a95ff41d91468120c","tid":1840224,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:46:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efa6b76a43c25ec16a6ac527bcafc10c54415313","tid":1840224,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:47:51.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"a37a50f2aeb55a14da7691e6b749d79ee9639771","tid":1840224,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:51:17.000Z","msg":"初三遲"},{"pid":"3c7ab4c84da9d943941102ff69041028109400ad","tid":1840224,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-2